However, I understand that my response was completely inappropriate and far exceeded acceptable behavior. Immediately after the incident, I realized the gravity of my actions and promptly took my employee to the nearest emergency room to ensure he received the necessary medical attention. I express sincere remorse for the pain and distress I caused to both the victim and his family.

